    </p>
    
    <div>
		<p id="my_name"><b id="my_name-1"><%= user.username %></b>
			<ul id="social">
				<li>
					<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/harshit-kumar-21060b165/" target="_blank"><img src="/images/linkedin-sign.png" title="linkedin"></a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="https://www.facebook.com/harshit.gera.106" target="_blank"><img src="/images/facebook-logo.png" title="facebook"></a>
